    <h2>Modern Development Practices</h2>

    <p>The way we approach web development has fundamentally changed. Gone are the days of monolithic applications and manual deployments. Today's developers embrace:</p>

    <ul>
        <li>Component-based architecture
            <ul>
                <li>React Components</li>
                <li>Vue Components</li>
                <li>Web Components</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>Serverless computing
            <ul>
                <li>AWS Lambda</li>
                <li>Vercel Functions</li>
                <li>Netlify Functions</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>Progressive Web Apps (PWAs)</li>
        <li>Microservices architecture</li>
    </ul>

